'''合成燃料'''({{lang|en|Synthetic fuel}}, 或 synfuel)是液體燃料，其獲得是來自[[煤|煤]]，[[天然氣|天然氣]]，[[油頁岩|油頁岩]]，或[[生物質|生物質]]。它也可以指燃料來自其他固體，如塑料或橡膠廢物。它也可能（不經常）指以類似的方式產生的氣體燃料。“合成燃料”術語常見用途的是描述燃料生產通過[[费托合成|费托合成]](Fischer–Tropsch process)<ref>{{cite web|title=Liquid Fuels - Fischer-Tropsch Synthesis|url=http://www.netl.doe.gov/research/Coal/energy-systems/gasification/gasifipedia/ftsynthesis|website=Gasifipedia|publisher=National Energy Technology Laboratory, U.S. Department of Energy|accessdate=25 July 2014|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220131813/http://www.netl.doe.gov/research/coal/energy-systems/gasification/gasifipedia/ftsynthesis|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[甲醇|甲醇]]汽油轉換<ref>{{cite web|title=Liquid Fuels - Conversion of Methanol to Gasoline|url=http://www.netl.doe.gov/research/Coal/energy-systems/gasification/gasifipedia/methanol-to-gasoline|website=Gasifipedia|publisher=National Energy Technology Laboratory, U.S. Department of Energy|accessdate=25 July 2014|archive-date=2014-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140717225057/http://www.netl.doe.gov/research/Coal/energy-systems/gasification/gasifipedia/methanol-to-gasoline|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，或直接[[煤液化|煤液化]]燃料<ref>{{cite web|title=Liquid Fuels - Direct Liquefaction Processes|url=http://www.netl.doe.gov/research/Coal/energy-systems/gasification/gasifipedia/direct-liquefaction|website=Gasifipedia|publisher=National Energy Technology Laboratory, U.S. Department of Energy|accessdate=25 July 2014|archive-date=2014-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140725082303/http://www.netl.doe.gov/research/Coal/energy-systems/gasification/gasifipedia/direct-liquefaction|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

至2009年7月，世界各地的商業合成燃料生產量超過每天24萬桶（38000m3 / 日），新的建設或開發項目多。{{fact|time=2015-07-15}}

目前主要通过[[补贴|补贴]]获得生产，为将来[[石油|石油]]资源耗尽可能出现的[[能源危机|能源危机]]提供解决方案。但由于[[煤炭|煤炭]]和[[天然气|天然气]]也是[[不可再生能源|不可再生能源]]，所以[[能源危机|能源危机]]并没有因此而获得真正解决。{{fact|time=2015-07-15}}

